Anita Asiimwe Bụ Minista nke Rwandan na ọkachamara na ahụike ọha na eze. Kemgbe ọnwa Ọktọba 2017, ọ bụ onye nhazi mba nke National Early Childhood Development Program.
Ọ bụkwa otu n'ime ndị guzobere Africa Constituency Bureau, Advocacy na CCMs Coordinating Body nke na-akwado olu ndị Afrịka na Global Fund megide HIV, TB na Malaria
